# Privacy Policy

Last updated: August 11, 2025

The **All-in-One Pi App** respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data.

## 1. Information We Collect
We may collect:
- Basic account information (username, email)
- Usage data (how you interact with the app)
- Device data (browser type, OS)

## 2. How We Use Your Data
We use your data to:
- Provide and improve our services
- Personalize your experience
- Communicate with you

## 3. Data Sharing
We **do not** sell your data. We may share limited information with trusted partners when necessary for service delivery.

## 4. Security
We implement industry-standard measures to protect your data.

## 5. Your Rights
You can request to update or delete your personal information at any time by contacting us at **onahchukwuemeka28@gmail.com**.

## 6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here with a revised "last updated" date.

